OL,3,CSauna users urged to hydrate to avoid
OL,4,Cheat stroke
OL,6,FSauna users have been urged to stay
OL,7,Fhydrated after a woman suffered severe
OL,8,Fheat stroke with multi-organ failure
OL,9,Fafter basking for too long in the heat.
OL,11,FExperts from Birmingham Heartlands
OL,12,FHospital described how a patient
OL,13,Fneeded hospital care for 12 days after
OL,14,Fheat stroke led to a number of serious
OL,15,Fhealth problems including a heart
OL,16,Fattack.
OL,18,FOnly around 10 cases of heat stroke
OL,19,Flinked to saunas have been documented.
