OL,6,FThe unnamed woman in her early 70s
OL,7,Falso had seizures, liver injury and
OL,8,Fkidney injury, among other conditions.
OL,10,FThe woman, a daily gym goer, was found
OL,11,Fin unconscious at an indoor sauna at
OL,12,Fher local gym.
OL,14,FBefore getting in the sauna she had
OL,15,Fbeen performing stretching exercises
OL,16,Ffor around 45 minutes.
OL,18,FParamedics found her with an extremely
OL,19,Fhigh core body temperature of 42C,
OL,20,Fvery low blood pressure and a fast
OL,21,Fheart rate.
