OL,6,FThe woman, who had a history of type 1
OL,7,Fdiabetes and thyroid problems, was
OL,8,Ftaken to the emergency department at
OL,9,FHeartlands.
OL,11,FShe was unresponsive and making
OL,12,Fgroaning noises and had a seizure in
OL,13,Fthe emergency department.
OL,15,FThe patient was cooled with wet towels
OL,16,Fand a fan when she was in the
OL,17,Femergency department, which saw her
OL,18,Fbody temperature return to normal
OL,19,Flevels, medics said.
