OL,6,FThe woman regained consciousness two
OL,7,Fhours after returning to normal body
OL,8,Ftemperature, but she was confused and
OL,9,Fdrowsy for two days.
OL,11,FFurther investigations revealed she
OL,12,Fhad suffered acute kidney injury `
OL,13,Fwhich had resolved 48 hours after she
OL,14,Fwas admitted to hospital.
OL,16,FOn the second day of her hospital
OL,17,Fstay, doctors found she had abnormal
OL,18,Fliver function.
OL,20,FShe was also found to have suffered a
OL,21,Fform of heart attack.
