OL,6,F"The most likely diagnosis was likely
OL,7,Fto be classical heat stroke with multi-
OL,8,Forgan failure," the doctors wrote in
OL,9,Fthe journal BMJ Case Reports.
OL,11,F"To the best of our knowledge, there
OL,12,Fhave been fewer than 10 previously
OL,13,Freported cases of heat stroke
OL,14,Fsecondary to sauna use," they said,
OL,15,Fincluding three deaths.
OL,17,FMedics saw the woman in hospital 26
OL,18,Fdays after the heat stroke and found
OL,19,Fshe had "returned to her baseline
OL,20,Fhealth status" but was still suffering
OL,21,Ffrom fatigue.
