OL,6,FThe patient said: "My experience has
OL,7,Femphasised the dangers of saunas and
OL,8,Fhow important it is to be fully
OL,9,Fhydrated on entering a sauna and for
OL,10,Fthem to be regularly checked by staff.
OL,12,F"As a regular sauna user I never
OL,13,Fsuffered any issues and, on
OL,14,Freflection, I believe I had not drunk
OL,15,Fenough water.
OL,17,F"I am pleased to say I'm feeling well
OL,18,Fand appear to have made a full
OL,19,Frecovery.
